Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是模擬彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到警告音響起還有誰能冷靜下來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.93,0:04:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,J1，你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心跳停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生緊急狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.94,0:04:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,J1駕駛員似乎因為某種原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.48,0:04:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在駕駛艙內死亡
