Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生緊急狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,J1駕駛員似乎因為某種原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.90,0:05:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在直升機內死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.74,0:05:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了以防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.84,0:05:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解除指令I.S
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依據指令S.A採取避難行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.61,0:05:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重複一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.61,0:05:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依據指令S.A採取避難行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.55,0:05:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,HA-01AV沒有解除指令I.S
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.52,0:05:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員的生命維持反應到現在仍全部正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然確認心跳已經停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.12,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於電子腦仍在發出生存信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以AI無視管制中心的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定優先保護駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並將避難行動解釋為外來攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，細腰蜂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久保田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荒卷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.46,0:06:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來事態緊急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.37,0:06:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要那裏有犯罪的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.87,0:06:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就會忍不住插手是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.62,0:06:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然目前告訴媒體說是實驗機種的空中加油訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但事實上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.92,0:06:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是政府為了配合最近即將實施的難民政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.53,0:06:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,近三年來最大規模同時也是在極機密狀態下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所舉行的實彈演習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出問題的直升機不是那架與美帝間的安保條約有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因涉嫌不法勾結而謠言四起的思考直升機嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.71,0:07:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是那一架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陸自也害怕被媒體攻擊(陸自，陸上自衛軍的簡稱）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.28,0:07:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以派出利用現有機體改良的AI輔助型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.48,0:07:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,俗稱「細腰蜂ADVANCE」的機種來參與演習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事件的起因則始終認定是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.02,0:07:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於駕駛員意外死亡所引發的一連串事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.23,0:07:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這個事態發展也太可疑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是瞞不過你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.47,0:07:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，你那邊掌握到什麼程度了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.81,0:07:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實彈演習時輔助型反戰車直升機的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.98,0:07:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在演習中倒下是上午5時57分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.58,0:07:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來在輔助AI的自動駕駛之下似乎已經平安無事的直升機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻無視於管制中心的解除命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.52,0:07:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在6時3分朝招慰難民居住區上空飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且在這之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.39,0:07:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輔助AI同時侵入航空母艦上的兩架同型機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及一架空中加油機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.80,0:08:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,共計三架於6時12分飛離航空母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.11,0:08:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各機在難民居住區上空會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.94,0:08:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說目前仍在電波發射塔上面盤旋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大致上都是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.78,0:08:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此外，有未確認的情報顯示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.72,0:08:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,淡路駐地有2架和歌山駐地有3架同型直升機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.05,0:08:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被輔助AI以聯機誘導方式在無人的狀況下飛走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到聯絡的各基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.36,0:08:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然立刻將同型機的AI切換為自閉模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是處理慢半拍的伊丹基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.57,0:08:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有兩架跟在後面飛走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.41,0:08:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能是以輔助AI為目標的計算機恐怖活動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.68,0:08:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突破軍方的防壁嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情報部也發現到有恐怖活動的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.45,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經拘留輔助AI的全體開發人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.62,0:08:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且進行各項調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻什麼都沒有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.53,0:09:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能是軍隊內部反彈引發的武裝叛變嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.63,0:09:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是受個別主義者的影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.77,0:09:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我甚至懷疑過是不是那些加入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.67,0:09:15.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聖母悼歌：Stabat Mater 自稱千禧年的某藝術家製作並發起的CyberDome Game\N通過向全體觀眾電子腦內移入軟體程序產生互動性影像空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.67,0:09:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前成為媒體抨擊目標的「聖母悼歌」享樂集團的隊員們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.01,0:09:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所犯下的罪行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是那個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.92,0:09:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在上面正在拚命想辦法用意外事故這個理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.49,0:09:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把事情解決掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.89,0:09:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所幸攻擊直升機只在電波發射塔上空盤旋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.89,0:09:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是能這樣解決就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民...嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就是這樣，少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.70,0:09:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我們掌握到的情報差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.64,0:09:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，現場好像在縣警機動隊控制之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是逐漸開始騷動的難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.05,0:09:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就連前來收拾局面的陸自機動部隊也被擋在外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.29,0:10:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,縣警就像是挺身出來主張難民居住區由自己管轄一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.22,0:10:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是難看死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.42,0:10:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直無藥可救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.76,0:10:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然先派托古薩和石川去調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在飛行中死亡的那位駕駛員的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.63,0:10:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我們該怎麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.63,0:10:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就要到達難民居住區了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠近現場後先待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.94,0:10:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事我們要不要出面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.51,0:10:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必須等總理最後的判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.78,0:10:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.58,0:10:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛剛說的不可以洩漏出去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.92,0:10:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光是被人看到我跟你坐在這裏就會很麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.09,0:10:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還拋不掉陞官的願望嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.36,0:10:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉，我沒辦法像你那樣過生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.36,0:10:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.10,0:10:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您是公安9課的荒卷先生吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.44,0:11:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內閣情報廳戰略影響調查會議代表輔佐官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田一人..(Hitori)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田一人(Kazundo，同字不同音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.42,0:11:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很少遇到有人能念對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.86,0:11:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我不覺得這個名字很特殊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.66,0:11:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，現在我開始覺得這是一個很好的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為只要說一次對方往往都能記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特別是跟這張臉一起說的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.77,0:11:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼內閣情報廳找我有何貴幹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.11,0:11:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於現在發生的這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.98,0:11:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想請你們公安9課協助解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.45,0:11:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然知道這樣很失禮但還是直接來拜訪您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想您應該知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們內閣情報廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.03,0:11:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,位於官房長官之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.87,0:11:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一個以收集、分析國內外情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.00,0:11:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且偶爾做點輿論操縱工作為主要活動的機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.97,0:12:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望您能將這次的事當作官房長官親自下的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟以首相的危機管理能力來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.85,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法期待她能夠當機立斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.25,0:12:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個有多大的供油能力?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果規格和以前一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汽車可以連續開六年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使吃油超兇的細腰蜂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.36,0:12:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面裝載的燃料應該也夠讓它連續飛行10個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.40,0:13:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，像那樣分給全部機體的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.23,0:13:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,單純數字上的計算每一架應該還能飛1小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.41,0:13:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以細腰蜂通常續航時間為2.5小時來計算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.84,0:13:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它們還能飛行的極限應該已經不到1個小時了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.32,0:13:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個油桶有沒有可能先掉下來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.55,0:13:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大甲蟲會最後才掉下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.36,0:13:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為它自己會越來越輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,續航時間也會延長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特先生，我問你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.60,0:13:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙和我們一樣都是AI對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.10,0:13:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛，聽說充其量只是以有人駕駛為前提的輔助型AI
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話雖然這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.21,0:13:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然現在沒人在上面它應該算是靠自己思考在飛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.35,0:13:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它們真的非常不喜歡現有的工作條件呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.65,0:13:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍隊的工作條件那麼差嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.82,0:13:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個性灰暗的AI真的很容易抓狂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.29,0:14:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我們還是得依照命令跟它們作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.03,0:14:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反戰車直升機應該算是我們的天敵吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特先生，巴特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.34,0:14:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們肚子痛，可以先回去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.24,0:14:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的肚子在哪裏啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.09,0:14:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陸自那些傢伙靠太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.96,0:14:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想潛入輔助AI結果失敗了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.87,0:14:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陸自駕駛員的薪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像真的很低呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.14,0:15:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.51,0:15:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事情了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.85,0:15:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然特地跑到現場來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.15,0:15:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也就是說總理手上的韁繩還沒鬆開?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.59,0:15:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，我先跟你說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.89,0:15:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是內閣情報廳的官員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.83,0:15:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰略影響調查會議的合田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.36,0:15:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先說結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.03,0:15:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從現在起為了解決本次事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.17,0:15:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現場指揮權全面移交給我們公安9課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過這次作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.14,0:15:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你們完全依照他擬定的方法執行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.48,0:15:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老爹，你瘋了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.45,0:16:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們留在9課可不是為了當政府養的狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據我們的計算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.75,0:16:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,48分鐘後第一架直升機就會墜毀在難民居住區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.93,0:16:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了那個地步事情將無可挽回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.46,0:16:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這很明顯已經是恐怖活動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就聽聽你的作戰計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很高興你誠實面對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.18,0:16:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你完全相信那傢伙說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為何答應他的要求?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.25,0:16:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員暴斃和AI的失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.15,0:16:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算與恐怖活動無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是直升機如果墜毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.92,0:16:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必然會給這一帶造成一定的損害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.99,0:16:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那時候難民的動向很難說不會變成危險的火藥庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.56,0:16:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何況沒有那傢伙給的情報我們原本就沒有解決方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.10,0:16:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想說的是我們的立場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.77,0:16:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了，不說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齋藤，準備好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.71,0:17:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.71,0:17:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.16,0:17:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是會動的東西不管是什麼都加以攻擊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.26,0:17:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以下到地面上喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.80,0:18:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是被空對地飛彈鎖定就逃不掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.16,0:18:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形勢不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.56,0:18:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不但二對一 而且火力原本就比不上它們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.48,0:18:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，跟那傢伙說的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.32,0:18:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特，目標機體跟過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.19,0:18:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已確認目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.84,0:19:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，通過正面的時候請讓目標稍微抬起下巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.08,0:19:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了不破壞AI而只擊中駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想從駕駛座擋風玻璃側面貫穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.65,0:19:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.85,0:19:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.70,0:20:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受管制中心發出的作戰指令解除命令了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.44,0:20:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,預測沒有出錯真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.28,0:21:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要切斷心臟停止的駕駛員電子腦所發出的訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.22,0:21:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輔助AI應該就會接受管制中心發出的作戰指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.12,0:21:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我委託你們處理本案的眼光也非常正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.76,0:21:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多虧了你們，讓自衛官們不必背負殺害同僚的污名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你的意思是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.27,0:21:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們9課的齋藤背負污名就沒關係羅?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.30,0:21:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特，我早就習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.58,0:21:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛已經確認11架全部返航了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.96,0:21:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽過托古薩的報告了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.09,0:21:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那個駕駛員的家裏發現了心臟病的藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.06,0:21:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他似乎對長官隱瞞了病情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.40,0:21:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼少校，你是認為這件事並非他說的恐怖活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.57,0:22:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充其量只是意外?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.27,0:22:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.64,0:22:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有將找到的藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.41,0:22:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟暴斃駕駛員的血液做成分分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.61,0:22:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本沒有辦法確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.02,0:22:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內閣情報廳出現的時機彷彿他們早就知道一切真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.49,0:22:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有只是惡作劇般地挑起難民的反感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.43,0:22:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著擺出一副那就是真正目的的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從他們頭上飛走的陸自直升機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.60,0:22:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底意味著什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定在我們不知道的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.01,0:22:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一樁大型的犯罪已經開始萌芽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.58,0:23:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.28,0:23:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.76,0:23:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.79,0:23:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的美麗事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.06,0:23:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.57,0:23:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音——醒來吧
